 INSTALL               notes
 ruby/install          rsync src to site-lib
 ruby/install symlink  link to src from site-lib
 export RUBYLIB=ruby   just add dir to Ruby PATH
 gem install infod     a probably older and more-stable isotope

 EXTRAS
 bundle install  (in ruby/ pull in optional RDF libs)
 apt-get install ruby-tmail graphicsmagick libimage-exiftool-perl libid3-tools source-highlight man2html thin

 CONFIG
 mkdir -p http://hostname && cp -a {css,js} http://hostname

 DAEMON        notes
 infod         standalone
   ''  apache  sh/.htaccess
   ''  nginx   sh/nginx
 infod lo -d   listen only on localhost and go to background

